    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "あれくらいのタイムロスでライブに影響はありませんよ\n{user}さんは心配性ですね",
      "startTime": 118.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "Xmas-stage",
      "startTime": 121.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_03_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、天動さん。お疲れ様\nリハよかったよ。本番もよろしくな",
      "startTime": 124.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmasvenue-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "Xmas-stage",
      "startTime": 127.3666666667
    },
    {
